Read asset_normalizer.py (lines 771-800)
The extract_enrichment_uid returns resource_uid which is the short format. The assets_by_uid dict is keyed by ARN. We need to normalize the short UID to ARN. The fix is simple — try both the raw uid AND derive the ARN from the instance ID embedded in the short uid:

