Read resource_classifier.py (lines 335-394)
So the classifier loads root/dependent classification from a pythonsdk database (not the inventory or check DB). It queries operations and services tables in threat_engine_pythonsdk.

The log said: "Loaded 1742 discovery ops for CSP=aws (1568 root, 174 dependent)"

So ec2.describe_instances must be classified as dependent (174 dependent includes it). That's why it's in the enrichment path.

